---
export interface Props {}
---

<style>
  :root {
    --primary: #fff;
    --background: #f8f6f3;
    --text: #fff;
    --accent: #fff;
    --highlight-bg: #fff4f0;
    --table-bg: #fff;
    --table-alt-bg: #fdf2f2;
  }
  .exceptional-section {
    width: 100vw;
    margin-left: calc(50% - 50vw);
    margin-right: calc(50% - 50vw);
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
  }
  
  .exceptional-text-content {
    background: #285F73;
    padding: 6rem 2rem;
    color: var(--text);
  }
  
  .exceptional-bg-image {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
  }
  
  .bg-img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    display: block;
  }
  
  .exceptional-content {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 3rem;
  }
  .exceptional-heading {
    font-size: 2.75rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: var(--primary);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }
  .narrative-block {

    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    font-size: 1.125rem;
  }
  .comparison-container {
    overflow-x: auto;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }
  .comparison-table {

    border-collapse: collapse;
  }
  .comparison-table td {
    padding: 0.5rem;
    text-align: left;
  }
  .comparison-table td:first-child {
    font-weight: 500;
  }
  .cta {

    margin-top: 4rem;
  }
  .btn-primary {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
    background: #000;
    color: var(--accent);
    border-radius: 0.5rem;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 600;
    transition: background 0.3s ease;
  }
  .btn-primary:hover {
    background: #800000;
  }
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .exceptional-section {
      width: 100vw;
      margin-left: calc(50% - 50vw);
      margin-right: calc(50% - 50vw);
      
      background-position: center top;
    }
    .exceptional-text-content {
      padding: 4rem 1rem;
    }
    
    .bg-img {
      height: 100%;
      min-height: 400px;
    }
    .exceptional-heading { 
      font-size: 2rem; 
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }
    .narrative-block { 
      font-size: 1rem; 
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }
    .comparison-table {
      font-size: 0.9rem;
    }
    .comparison-table td {
      padding: 0.4rem;
    }
  }
  @media (min-width: 640px) and (max-width: 1024px) {
    .exceptional-section {
     
    }
    .exceptional-heading { font-size: 3rem; }
    .narrative-block { font-size: 1.125rem; }
  }
  @media (min-width: 1025px) {
    .exceptional-heading { font-size: 3.5rem; }
    .narrative-block { font-size: 1.25rem; }
  }
</style>

<section class="exceptional-section">
  <div class="exceptional-text-content">
    <div class="exceptional-content">
      <h2 class="exceptional-heading">Exceptional Value</h2>

      <div class="narrative-block">
        Picture this: a sleek studio in Dubai, lights humming, cameras rolling, at a price tag that could fund an entire week of shooting in Europe. Now imagine swapping that glare of skyscrapers for the tranquil peaks around Bishkek—same top-tier equipment, same seasoned crew, but with costs trimmed by more than half.
      </div>

      <div class="comparison-container">
        <table class="comparison-table">
          <tr>
            <td><strong>Expense</strong></td>
            <td><strong>Dubai</strong></td>
            <td><strong>Bishkek</strong></td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>Studio Day Rental</td>
            <td>$5,000</td>
            <td>$1,500</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>Camera Package (per day)</td>
            <td>$1,200</td>
            <td>$350</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>Crew Rate (pp/day)</td>
            <td>$2,000</td>
            <td>$500</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>Post-Production Suite</td>
            <td>$3,000</td>
            <td>$900</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td><strong>Total Budget</strong></td>
            <td><strong>$100,000</strong></td>
            <td><strong>$40,000</strong></td>
          </tr>
        </table>
      </div>

      <div class="narrative-block">
        Those savings aren't just numbers—they're extra shooting days, upgraded talent, and creative freedom. In Bishkek, your vision takes front and center, not your overheads.
      </div>

      <div class="cta">
        <a href="/contact" class="btn-primary">Get Your Custom Quote</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="exceptional-bg-image">
    <img src="/photos/Exceptional-bg.jpg" alt="Exceptional value background" class="bg-img" />
  </div>
</section>